      "combat_options": { "type": "list", "nullable": true, "item_schema": {"name": "string", "value": "number"} }
    },
    "rules": [
      "sequence defines execution order — reorder steps as tactics demand",
      "Most turns use at most one move and one action",
      "action MUST be one of the available actions — NOT an ability name",
      "action/targets/move_to can all be null (narrative-only turn)",
      "melee actions require the target to be in the SAME zone — move first if needed",
      "ranged actions require the target to be within weapon range",
      "ready REPLACES your entire turn — use sequence [\"ready\"] with action, targets, and trigger",
      "delay REPLACES your entire turn — use sequence [\"delay\"] to hold your position in initiative"
    ]
